Sentencas: Tubular solid oxide fuel cells were fabricated and evaluated for their microstructure and electrochemical performance.
Titulo: High performance anode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by a novel slurry-casting method

Sentencas: The tubular substrate was prepared by casting NiO-Y2O3 stabilized ZrO2 (YSZ) slurry on the inner wall of a plastic mold (tube).
Titulo: High performance anode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by a novel slurry-casting method

Sentencas: The wall thickness and uniformity were controlled by slurry viscosity and rotation speed of the tube.
Titulo: High performance anode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by a novel slurry-casting method

Sentencas: The cells consisted of Ni-YSZ functional anode, YSZ electrolyte and (La0.8Sr0.2)(0.95)MnO3-delta (LSM)-YSZ cathode prepared in sequence on the substrate by dip-coating and sintering.
Titulo: High performance anode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by a novel slurry-casting method

Sentencas: Their dimension was 50 mm in length, 0.8 mm in thickness and 10.5 mm in outside diameter.
Titulo: High performance anode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by a novel slurry-casting method

Sentencas: The peak power density of the cell at temperatures between 650 and 850 degrees C was in the range from 85 to 522 mW cm(-2) and was greatly enhanced to the range from 308 to 1220 mW cm(-2) by impregnating PdO into LSM-YSZ cathode.
Titulo: High performance anode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by a novel slurry-casting method

Sentencas: During a cell testing at 0.7 A cm(-2) and 750 degrees C for 282 h, the impregnated PdO particles grew by coalescence, which increased the cathode polarization resistance and so that decreased the cell performance.
Titulo: High performance anode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by a novel slurry-casting method

Sentencas: According to the degradation tendency, the cell performance will be stabilized in a longer run.
Titulo: High performance anode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by a novel slurry-casting method
